ing: 1 (15 ounce) can cannellini beans, drained and rinsed
des: "This is a tasty, low-fat dip that is great with assorted veggies, crackers, and pita chips. I recommend letting it chill overnight to allow the flavors to develop.  "
ins: Place yogurt, feta, beans, garlic, and lemon juice in the bowl of your food processor and blend until smooth.  Add parsley, dill, chives, mint, and pepper; pulse until they are well combined. Transfer dip to serving bowl and chill until ready to serve.
